items.title: 8 Leadership Lessons from 8 Great Leaders
items.headline: Learning from the giants before us
objectives_summary: No leader is identical to another. And no one can replicate someone else's actions and get the same results. Yet, we learn so much from studying those who walked the same path before us. This course aims to stage a brief encounter with great leaders from the corporate world, hoping that by finding out one lesson from each of them would give you some ideas on how best you can take that in and utilise it in your leadership journey.
